data.text:
When William Gibson was born on 1 August 1832, in Ohio, United States, his father, Jacob Gibson, was 35 and his mother, Mary Gault, was 34. He married Mary Leistensnider on 11 June 1857, in Ashland, Ohio, United States. They were the parents of at least 4 sons and 5 daughters. He lived in Clear Creek MM, Ashland, Ohio, United States for about 30 years. He died on 27 June 1882, in Ashland, Ohio, United States, at the age of 49, and was buried in Savannah, Ashland, Ohio, United States.
